Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}命运也是推理的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}神秘的事件也能看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:07.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}久违了的洋子登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}偶像们也有很多烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在找寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.46,0:00:26.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经习惯了谎言 现在也是一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有能够确定的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使一个人也不能哭泣 软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.55,0:00:51.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Oh yeah. You're going nowhere. It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}切实地前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.77,0:01:28.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}感受现在 you're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}L－O－V－E
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.11,0:01:45.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}I love Yoko
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}洋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.60,0:01:52.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}从一大早开始 就反复看了好几次这卷录影带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k299}适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.63,0:02:01.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有什么不好啊 反正也是闲着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是来了好多邮件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}也许是有人要委托办案呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k215}我等一下再看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}你给我放在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看不是没事干 而是根本不想做事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.59,0:02:24.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯…电费账单 演讲的邀请函 报社的约稿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是洋子小姐寄来的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.23,0:02:28.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是晚会请柬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说是在她朋友家里举行的订婚仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}订…订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这次订婚的是她一个朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}是她说一定要见见毛利名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.93,0:02:55.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你会去的吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.46,0:03:00.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}订婚 订婚 订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来他都没有听进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:11.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}偶像们的秘密（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.14,0:03:15.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不不不 这真是我的荣幸啊 洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.98,0:03:20.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没想到能够参加你朋友的订婚晚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 不 感到荣幸的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}冒昧地邀请您来 真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}您一定很惊讶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}不 一点都没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k245}说得还真好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}之前错以为是洋子订婚 还消沉了那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}话说回来 是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你的那个要订婚的密友是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}见到了就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}她可是大家都认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.93,0:03:43.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}都认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.24,0:03:44.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k131}洋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:46.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}真的被你请来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}名侦探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.74,0:04:00.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是不是就是 演侦探左文字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}剑崎修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.48,0:04:10.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 你的那个订婚的密友就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 我是那个男主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.78,0:04:17.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}洋子的密友是那个要嫁给我的女主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真没想到你能请到毛利名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她肯定会很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实我还没有告诉她这件事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k299}想给她一个惊喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.42,0:04:33.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}那我们可要好好欣赏一下她惊讶的表情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.52,0:04:40.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没人来应门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家应该都已经到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}门根本就没上锁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:53.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}特意赶来却被我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:12.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不不 被你这个当红女演员打 真是三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最近我被跟踪狂所困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.76,0:05:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}刚才又在猫眼里看到一个陌生的男人往里看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:20.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以我才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}邀请人家来 好歹要知道长相啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那 要和剑崎先生订婚的洋子小姐的密友就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯 就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}正式的结婚仪式在明年春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还没有告诉新闻记者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.43,0:05:42.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说起来薰小姐和剑崎先生共同演过侦探左文字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯 的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我正打算今天晚上播那部戏的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.18,0:05:50.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}和大家一起一边祝福 一边要好好的逗一逗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这对甜蜜的小两口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是岳野雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k173}你的指甲还是这么漂亮啊 小雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个假指甲不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}冲野洋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}岳野雪 草野薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有一个人 四个就全部到齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}唉呀 真是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦 谁在叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}辉美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}辉美也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 洋子非要让我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嫌我碍事我就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.15,0:06:39.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}别这样 好不容易地球少女的四个人凑齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.98,0:06:40.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}地球少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k173}你当然不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.51,0:06:47.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}草野薰是草的香气 代表大草原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.31,0:06:51.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}岳野雪是崇山峻岭上的皑皑白雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.41,0:06:55.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}星野辉美是闪耀夜空的满天群星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:07:00.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而冲野洋子则是波光粼粼的蓝色海洋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以四个人合起来就是地球少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.53,0:07:11.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k119}四个人的名字的确都包含了地球上的美景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过因为辉美跟小薰不和 地球少女就解散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在还在唱歌的只剩下洋子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过我真的没想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.44,0:07:26.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}四个人之中 最小的薰却最先结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.69,0:07:27.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也没想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}原以为最先结婚的是辉美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说起来 辉美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}你不是说你有心上人了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}是啊是啊 和那个人怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}告白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k255}什么也没发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.29,0:07:43.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k99}与其结婚走进人生的坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.35,0:07:50.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不如单相思一直远远的望着对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样美梦也不会破灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}喂 你什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}辉…辉美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}话说回来 那是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}那个带孩子的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}是啊是啊 不会是剑崎的哥哥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不…那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.17,0:08:08.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}侦探左文字就快开演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家不去看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}我不想看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}我想先去洗个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}等播完后再来叫我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}不过 刚做的菜要凉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最好还是大家一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}废话真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k112}我说不看就不看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.51,0:08:32.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}你这个被别人淘汰的人还没有资格教我怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.19,0:08:34.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}喂 小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她还是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}只要是她演的戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}她就会不好意思跟大家一起看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}计划执行得很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}喂 真的要那么做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}当然了 所以才叫你来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k182}那我就先在客厅里等着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}洋子你就先去洗手间换衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.55,0:09:01.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.11,0:09:15.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这不就是地球少女初次登台时候穿的衣服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:16.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}等薰小姐从浴室出来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k82}我们三个就会穿着这套衣服 唱当年出道时候的歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}作为我们送给小薰的祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}不过 穿成这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}现在还真有点不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}很好很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}非常漂亮 洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k245}你的反应也太过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}（我到这里的时候其实它就已经坏掉了…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.00,0:09:40.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 你们真的要进行那个计划啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 下一个是我返老还童了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你快一点 我还没有换衣服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们趁现在来写卡片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k267}大家都写上对小薰的祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}祝你永远幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.20,0:10:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}下一个 辉美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}我就算了 不写了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这正好是你们和好的机会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}薰姐姐真的说过她很想见毛利叔叔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 她刚才不也说过嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}她现在被跟踪狂所困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}很想阻止这样的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过算了 等我搬来这里住以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}我看那个家伙恐怕就不敢靠近了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.63,0:10:43.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们在写祝福吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}嗯 大家各写一句祝福吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 我去换衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等…等一下 这是写的什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.88,0:11:01.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}（节哀顺变 星野辉美）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}“节哀顺变”的后面还点上香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}很有她的特色嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然辉美用烟灰 那我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}唇…唇印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}该你了 经纪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}你也写几句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}不用了 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你就不要客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}什么都行 埋怨她也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.93,0:11:44.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k119}如果你这么不愿意的话就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}不 我只是太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好了 我已经换好衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.33,0:11:58.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k173}那我就去叫薰出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.32,0:12:18.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}结果根本没有一个人认真看我的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}算了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}那首歌已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}就只等小薰过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.00,0:12:29.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小薰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:34.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k97}那个…怎么叫都没有回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是不是在浴室里晕倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样的话 剑崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}赶紧去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看她八成又是闹别扭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是…血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}一直到玄关那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}喂 薰 快出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}大家都等着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}剑崎先生 快把门打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}薰 我进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.82,0:13:25.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.29,0:13:28.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}还有脉搏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}马上送医院可能还有救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 怎么了 怎么这么吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}振作点 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}兰 去叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}伤者叫做草野薰 现年20岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是28楼的1号房吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.86,0:14:10.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是20岁的女孩怎么一个人住在这么高级的公寓里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是谁家的千金小姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}啊 你不知道她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}以前的地球少女成员…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}地球 那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.10,0:14:19.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}我们是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k114}请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}我们好像走错房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}目暮警部 你可终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}全是演艺界的大明星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.14,0:14:43.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k103}那么 我再来确认一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}你们三个人来参加薰小姐的订婚晚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为了给她一个惊喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}在她洗澡的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}在洗手间按顺序换了刚才穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}按照洋子 雪 辉美的顺序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接着 在三个人换完衣服以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.56,0:15:11.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}经纪人间熊先生去浴室叫她却没有回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后是她的未婚夫剑崎先生去叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}打开了浴室门之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.56,0:15:22.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}发现薰小姐颈部出血昏倒在浴池里 是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.53,0:15:29.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后 又是一次恶魔般的偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}招致了这不幸事件的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}警部大人把我说得像是瘟神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.56,0:15:38.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是接到了洋子小姐的邀请 偶然来到现场而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是偶尔 而是常常吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么受伤的薰小姐现在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被救护车送到杯户医院去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:54.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}陪着去的间熊先生还没打电话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还不知道情况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}小薰 可不能死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.96,0:16:01.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}我打个电话去医院问问吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}那我跟你一起去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}我爸爸在那里治疗糖尿病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以我知道那里的电话号码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}哦 那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.02,0:16:21.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}割伤薰小姐的脖子的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}会不会就在这群人里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.04,0:16:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}这不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:30.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}不过老话不是说过 第一发现者嫌疑最大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂喂 我没有理由杀她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我在浴室发现她的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}那个戴眼镜的小男孩也在旁边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.03,0:16:43.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}是这个小男孩让我开门 我才开的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.99,0:16:44.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k131}嗯 因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:51.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}从走廊到玄关之间有很多血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我把大门打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k278}就发现那些东西掉在门外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.11,0:17:05.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是雨衣 全是破洞的线手套 空眼药水瓶和手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}本来是放在门外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}在急救人员来之前 拿到屋子里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雨衣 线手套都沾满了血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该是犯人留下的东西没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}手帕上还有一点口红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果这瓶子里面是麻醉药的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}可能是犯人在割伤她的颈部之前 喷在手帕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}捂住她的鼻子 麻醉了她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}可是 到底是谁对薰小姐下的毒手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}骚扰她的那个跟踪狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}就是那个品质恶劣 乱按门铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}一直困扰薰的人干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.41,0:17:49.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}乱按门铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}就是按了人家门铃就跑的恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}薰遇到的不是简单的恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}奇怪的信每次都放在玄关外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}“还会再来”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}“下次还会再来”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}“死了也会再来”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}那个人每来一次 信的内容就越来越恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}信是用打字机打的 看了就令人感到毛骨悚然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.46,0:18:24.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}所以薰小姐才会在我按门铃的时候用球拍打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}案发的时候玄关上锁了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}门是开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.18,0:18:32.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}可能是因为我们人比较多很放心 所以就没锁门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.66,0:18:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说那个跟踪狂发现门没上锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}偷偷潜入室内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}正巧遇到从浴室里出来的薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为薰小姐看见了他的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.94,0:18:47.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}他就用麻醉剂麻醉了她 用刀刺伤了她的颈部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.01,0:18:52.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k96}因为雨衣 手套上的血太引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就脱下来扔在大门外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.45,0:18:57.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}然后就逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.72,0:18:59.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}在这栋大楼周围展开调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.86,0:19:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}现在没有下雨 犯人却穿着雨衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}很可能会有人注意到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.38,0:19:09.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}可是 我觉得应该不会有人看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为那个人非常小心谨慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}小心谨慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.21,0:19:18.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.94,0:19:22.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k73}要是穿着沾满鲜血的雨衣逃跑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}总会不小心踩到掉在地上的血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}可是我看的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}门口滴落了很多血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}却一点都没有被踩到的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.72,0:19:36.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}这就说明犯人逃走的时候 是小心谨慎地躲着血迹走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}但是还是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k297}如果说犯人小心谨慎的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}他看见玄关门口那么多双鞋 就应该知道屋里有很多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么还要进来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}警…警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.27,0:19:56.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}该不会犯人是把沾满血迹的雨衣拿在手里移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}故意让血滴到地板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.77,0:20:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}然后将雨衣扔在门口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样就可以让人以为他逃到外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.83,0:20:10.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 而且如果犯人和薰小姐认识的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要把薰小姐从浴室叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}在她毫无戒备的情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.45,0:20:19.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}用麻醉剂弄晕她 是非常简单的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.38,0:20:21.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}难道说犯人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可能就在我们之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我说得没错吧 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}辉美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}确实如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.75,0:20:43.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我们换衣服的洗手间就在大家聊天的客厅和浴室之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}想悄悄地杀了她也不是不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.03,0:20:47.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k299}小雪也这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}就算真是如此 洋子小姐也不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她换衣服的时候 我们几个就在洗手间外面等她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那之后我们就一直待在客厅 没有离开过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.46,0:21:00.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}那么也不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}薰去洗澡的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}我和这小男孩在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}嗯 是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}薰姐姐去浴室的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}送她去的这位哥哥当然不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你也去了浴室的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.94,0:21:21.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}那个时候也可以袭击薰小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}我要先对每个人进行询问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.38,0:21:31.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在这之前 还有一样必须要找到的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.32,0:21:33.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}那把割开小薰喉咙的 类似于刀的物品
